{"tid":2210364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疫市奇招）扮賣switch同角落生物 油麻地實店呃左過百萬","createTime":"2020-09-20T10:57:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T05:26:34.000Z","uid":250419,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"da54ccbaad4aa232580378fdd729b94a6756914a","tid":2210364,"uid":250419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:57:15.000Z","msg":"實店係油麻地現時點既Dreamstar<br />\nIg fb carousell 都賣角落生物同switch game同機<br />\n人稱星哥星嫂既店主9月中走左佬<br />\n網上一堆苦主夾夾埋埋超過500人俾佢地呃左過百萬<br />\n<br />\n扮黃既店主好有手段 <br />\n你買幾樣野 佢會用要遊行 肺炎 落雨既藉口成日話冇貨 遲幾個星期又交其中一樣貨俾你<br />\n搞到你以為真係代理問題冇貨 又俾佢呃買多幾樣<br />\n<br />\n係既 樓豬都係蠢到俾佢地呃既一員<br />\n苦主招手區 大家夾計推推佢 雖然樓豬俾人呃既錢唔算多 但真係好撚委屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ad29fb3a069eee5db358aa61f2b14d220b4dd7","tid":2210364,"uid":86756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T11:01:12.000Z","msg":"實體店唔係一手交錢 <br />\n一手交貨？"},{"pid":"31f7bc286599dc7be7d780b1c777db5bdfa36fca","tid":2210364,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T11:01:24.000Z","msg":"係咪已經移咗民去英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15924923924af82346001f397a0a3b54156efbed","tid":2210364,"uid":250419,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"c8ad29fb3a069eee5db358aa61f2b14d220b4dd7","tid":2210364,"uid":86756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T11:01:12.000Z","msg":"實體店唔係一手交錢 <br />\n一手交貨？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T11:03:00.000Z","msg":"期貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話要訂 多數一個月有貨<br />\n訂之前見網上冇人負皮仲話收到 就信左佢"},{"pid":"21601c249d87810ae5a64c63e3e9e7fda863aa69","tid":2210364,"uid":250419,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"31f7bc286599dc7be7d780b1c777db5bdfa36fca","tid":2210364,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T11:01:24.000Z","msg":"係咪已經移咗民去